data.description: Sprawling 3000 sq ft pool home with guest house, sitting on 17,424 square feet of land! This house is well appointed with a solar heat system, metal roof and complimented with a propane powered generator system. This home is idea for someone seeking that ''not so close'' homesite, and has plenty of room for recreational toys. The detached guest house, has its own living area with bath and can be used as a pool house or private dwelling  for multigenerational families. There are far too many options to mention and the best way to see them all is to stop by. This is Fort Pierce at its best and located minutes to downtown, the beaches and fingers crossed, Brightline Station. Don't miss out on this HUGE property with all the trimmings!
